Items.mt: I don't care what happens to Cheng's board, but I am not a good person who repays grievances with virtue. I don't care what happens to Cheng's board, but I'm not a good person who repays kindness with kindness. Hey, if he wants to get the credit, it's too cheap for him not to put some stumbling blocks.
